data.description:
CHECK THIS OUT: 4 bedrooms 3+ baths with a full unfinished walkout basement (huge). Basement has a full bathroom that is almost completed. Doggie door in basement to back yard. Huge corner lot, large deck on back, 3 seasons room, below 3 seasons room a place for a hot tub with drain and electric, Slide placed off of deck for kids, Privacy fenced back yard, unfinished bonus room above garage, New appliances less than a year old (fridge, range, oven, dishwasher, microwave), Just replaced the AC unit so it's BRAND NEW, main level master bedroom with master bath and walk in closet. 1/2 bath on main floor. RV pad. No HOA to worry about! You will not find so many features for the price. The home can use updating, but it is move in ready and we reduced asking price to accommodate buyers for carpet, etc!  Call me to schedule a time to see the property as we are a couple hours away and will need to schedule for weekends likely. Work is ongoing and if continues we may up the price a bit the more we do. 
Willing to pay 3% BUYER agency fees. This is FSBO, but understand many people are using realtors. Thanks!
data.whatILove: We have lived in this home for 7 years and it's a quiet neighborhood great for kids. We are 1 block away from an elementary school, and our child walked to and from. Lots of children in area that play together. We are sad to move, but it was necessary for work, etc.
